      <title>本田考虑与日产合并 富士康也在竞购股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/foxconn-said-to-have-approached-nissan-to-take-controlling-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车公司已成为日本最新的收购目标，它正在探索与本田汽车公司的合并，并面临着来自台湾 iPhone 制造商富士康的鸿海精密工业股份有限公司的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/foxconn-said-to-have-approached-nissan-to-take-controlling-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 05:18:33 GMT</pubDate>
